- Custom icon
    - it is possible to set an app icon by creating assets/icon.png.
- Score should be how many changed tiles required
    4 -> 4 points, 1 -> 1 point 
- After 60sec -> bitrot
    - random change bit when added tile

- Credits:
    - SketchyLogic (music) OpenGameart.org

- Dynamic sprite size creation
    -> VBO id placement.

- FSM for state changes

